: 0.9683729442285419, \"rank\": 0.018517509755135338, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics closing ceremony\", \"from\": 247, \"to\": 294}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP China's central authorities sent a congratulatory message to the country's Olympic delegation on Sunday for their accomplishments and sportsmanship at the 2024 Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 344, \"end\": 349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999506488879816, \"rank\": 4.21246411360872e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"/CFP\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 342}, {\"ngram\": \"a congratulatory message\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 400}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's Olympic delegation\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"their accomplishments\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"sportsmanship\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 490}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have won glory for our country and people, and we extend warm congratulations and heartfelt compliments to you,\\\" read a message jointly sent by the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China (CPC) and the State Council, China's cabinet.\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 679, \"end\": 696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Committee_of_the_Chinese_Communist_Party\", \"score\": 0.9997723399205195, \"rank\": 0.00016049919614843106, \"text\": \"Central Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Committee_of_the_Chinese_Communist_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Committee_of_the_Chinese_Communist_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 730, \"end\": 733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Communist_Party\", \"score\": 0.999999977296284, \"rank\": 2.2649440890274278e-08, \"text\": \"CPC\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Communist_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Communist_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 743, \"end\": 756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Council_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\", \"score\": 0.9999999999961346, \"rank\": 2.982053333525173e-12, \"text\": \"State Council\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Council_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Council_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\"}, {\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999506488879816, \"rank\": 4.21246411360872e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"glory\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 545}, {\"ngram\": \"our country\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 561}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"warm congratulations\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 608}, {\"ngram\": \"heartfelt compliments\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 658}, {\"ngram\": \"the Communist Party\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 719}, {\"ngram\": \"China\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China finished second on the overall medal table at Paris 2024, with 40 gold, 27 silver and 24 bronze medals, marking the country's best performance at an overseas Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 954, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 776, \"end\": 781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999506488879816, \"rank\": 4.21246411360872e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the overall medal table\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 824}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 833}, {\"ngram\": \"40 gold\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"27 silver\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 863}, {\"ngram\": \"24 bronze medals\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's best performance\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 924}, {\"ngram\": \"an overseas Olympic Games\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have vigorously promoted the Chinese sports spirit and the Olympic spirit, striving to win medals not only for your athletic performance but also for your moral integrity, sportsmanship and clean competition,\\\" read the message.\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 990, \"end\": 997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.5571857420995323, \"rank\": 0.7867473471748975, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"your athletic performance\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"your moral integrity\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"sportsmanship\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"clean competition\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"the message\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have actively practiced the Olympic motto of 'Faster, Higher, Stronger \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 Together,' engaging in fair competition and friendly exchanges with athletes from around the world.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic motto\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"fair competition\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"friendly exchanges\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In doing so, you have enhanced your skills, deepened friendship and demonstrated China's strength, spirit and image to the world, spreading the voice and values of China.\\\"\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1451, \"end\": 1456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999506488879816, \"rank\": 4.21246411360872e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1534, \"end\": 1539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999506488879816, \"rank\": 4.21246411360872e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your skills\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"friendship\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"spirit\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"image\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"the voice\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1519}, {\"ngram\": \"values\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Your outstanding achievements and performances have further ignited the patriotism of Chinese people both at home and abroad, uplifted the national spirit and united the people towards progress,\\\" added the message.\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1630, \"end\": 1644, \"titl